{"tid":1174623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【借肚疑案】李家傑：修訂條例為堵塞漏洞 沒有理由不支持","createTime":"2019-05-28T03:45:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T05:49:21.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f2fa2338da6ba09a72b5605c10aaaf4630b3a13f","tid":1174623,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T03:45:38.000Z","msg":"宣布退任的恒地主席李兆基，出席股東會後連同兩名兒子李家傑及李家誠會見記者，被問及對《逃犯條例》修訂的看法，李家傑回應指，修訂條例是為了堵塞漏洞，看不到不支持的理由。<br />\n<br />\n被問到修例會否造成海外及內地投資者撤資，繼而拖累本港樓市及股市，李家傑回應指，這只是各人的猜測，認為沒有問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E6%9D%8E%E5%AE%B6%E5%82%91-%E4%BF%AE%E8%A8%82%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E7%82%BA%E5%A0%B5%E5%A1%9E%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E-%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E7%90%86%E7%94%B1%E4%B8%8D%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81-024500194.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%2582%2591-%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E8%25A8%2582%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%25A0%25B5%25E5%25A1%259E%25E6%25BC%258F%25E6%25B4%259E-%25E6%25B2%2592%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%2590%2586%25E7%2594%25B1%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581-024500194.html&d=4a077UaaKOqSfaiyS2iiQRV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=1df3ea95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E6%9D%8E%E5%AE%B6%E5%82%91-%E4%BF%AE%E8%A8%82%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E7%82%BA%E5%A0%B5%E5%A1%9E%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E-%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E7%90%86%E7%94%B1%E4%B8%8D%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81-024500194.html</a>"},{"pid":"1fb39bb93198e3854eb4e60f9c0eed5628a1385b","tid":1174623,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T03:54:00.000Z","msg":"睇黎係2邊落注<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c42b5f5ec6e3a59796b1f412b3bbbbe75e0978e2","tid":1174623,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T03:59:09.000Z","msg":"根據《人類生殖科技條例》，禁止在本港進行涉及商業成分的代母交易，受助對象亦僅限已婚夫婦進行；條文更列明，在香港或其他地方，提出或參與任何以代母安排為出發點的商議、要約或同意商議作代母安排而付款或接受付款，均屬違法，最高可判監兩年罰款十萬元。<br />\n<br />\n梁智鴻昨出席公開場合時卻指出，本港的法例十分清楚指明以代母產子不可涉及商業成分，亦只容許已婚父母利用代母產子；法例的精神是讓因基因或身體問題而不能生育的夫婦，可透過科學方法協助產子，因要好好保障嬰兒，故不容單身人士以代母產子。不過被問及港人在外國找代母生子是否犯法時，他直言：「我相信香港嘅法例好難伸到去外國！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20101030/00407_020.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthe-sun.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20101030%2F00407_020.html&d=4a077UaaKOqSfaiyS2iiQRV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=58023d75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20101030/00407_020.html</a>"},{"pid":"cf64452c7ebc6b2bfc7633847574732583eb0a91","tid":1174623,"uid":53481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T04:45:53.000Z","msg":"看不到不支持 邏輯上唔等同 支持<br />\n玩文字遊戲"},{"pid":"cafad4f0d795821560b4fa7d4e21c87401f01b0e","tid":1174623,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf64452c7ebc6b2bfc7633847574732583eb0a91","tid":1174623,"uid":53481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T04:45:53.000Z","msg":"看不到不支持 邏輯上唔等同 支持<br />\n玩文字遊戲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T04:49:00.000Z","msg":"語言偽術<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0ca33029a668fe6ba123efd7a7915200fc5c00d","tid":1174623,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T05:42:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b359f1e632a618972fc76d6e0b565a6c7828aac","tid":1174623,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T05:43:36.000Z","msg":"又買晒大細加圍骰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e845837fe8a430df36f36d2b273821b88195e92","tid":1174623,"uid":147367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"